==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Publishment
<hw>Pub"lish*ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
act or process of making publicly known; publication.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A public notice of intended marriage, required by
the laws of some States.</def> <mark>[U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Puccoon</ent>⟦br⟧
